Ubuntu 18.04 (Use third party)
1) Update the system (if not updated you might face issues while trying to install a new program). Can do it by:
   Software Updater (app)
   $ sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get upgrade
2) Install basic software:
   sudo apt-get install build-essential cmake git vim
   sudo apt-get install openjdk-11-jdk
3) Install basic applications
   chromium
   pycharm
   eclipse
   sublime
4) Install basic compilers
   anaconda3
   
